   "end": "0.080", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.240", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.360", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.880", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lieber Kollege M\u00fcller! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht ja gar nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle Selbstst\u00e4ndigen oder Solo-Selbstst\u00e4ndigen \u00fcber einen Kamm zu scheren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch Sie k\u00f6nnen doch nicht leugnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.040", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir eine ganze Reihe von massiven Problemen gerade in diesem Bereich haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.640", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann man besonders deutlich sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man sich einmal die Kultur- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Kreativwirtschaft anschaut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.280", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei geht es ja nicht nur um diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.320", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die immer in der ersten Reihe und im Rampenlicht stehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.280", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht auch um alle diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im hinteren Bereich daf\u00fcr sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.960", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Produktionen und vieles andere mehr stattfinden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.160", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht nicht um die Glitzerwelt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.080", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn diese hat in der Regel mit der sozialen Realit\u00e4t vieler Kulturschaffenden \u00fcberhaupt gar nichts zu tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.880", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb hat dieses Thema auch immer wieder das Parlament besch\u00e4ftigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich erinnere noch einmal daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die von dem k\u00fcrzlich verstorbenen sozialdemokratischen Bundesarbeitsminister Herbert Ehrenberg eingef\u00fchrte K\u00fcnstlersozialversicherung ein Meilenstein war\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wissen wir alle\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.200", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um mit der Absicherung im Krankheitsfall und der Alterssicherung \u00fcberhaupt auf den Weg zu kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.560", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir im Koalitionsvertrag festgehalten haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.400", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns f\u00fcr den Erhalt der K\u00fcnstlersozialversicherung einsetzen und pr\u00fcfen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "inwieweit sich die Besch\u00e4ftigungsverh\u00e4ltnisse ver\u00e4ndert haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.480", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit k\u00f6nnen wir den neuen Herausforderungen in diesem Bereich gerecht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist eine ganz wichtige sozialpolitische Entscheidung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.680", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es au\u00dferdem gut und sinnvoll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.000", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die in der letzten Woche noch gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrende Bundesregierung beschlossen hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Gesetzentwurf einzubringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der eine bestehende Sonderregelung in der Arbeitslosenversicherung f\u00fcr die kurzfristig Besch\u00e4ftigten erst einmal verl\u00e4ngert hat; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ansonsten w\u00e4re diese Regelung am 31.\u00a0Juli ausgelaufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit haben wir erst einmal die Mindeststandardsicherung weiter geregelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.160", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage aber auch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist kein Ja bis zum Jahr\u00a02021. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.960", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind absolut gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.240", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "uns sehr schnell und sehr intensiv mit dieser Regelung auseinanderzusetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.200", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute sprechen alle Daten und Zahlen daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.840", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir dort geregelt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.320", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht so ganz funktionieren kann; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn sonst h\u00e4tten im Zeitraum von 2015 bis 2016 nicht nur 239\u00a0Antr\u00e4ge auf Arbeitslosengeld bewilligt werden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss man ganz klar feststellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.800", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Regelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach der man heute in einem Engagement nicht l\u00e4nger als 10\u00a0Wochen befristet besch\u00e4ftigt sein darf bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.280", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Westen nicht mehr als 3\u00a0045\u00a0Euro oder im Osten nicht mehr als 2\u00a0695\u00a0Euro verdienen darf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Anspr\u00fcche geltend zu machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.320", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat mit der Realit\u00e4t nichts mehr zu tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.800", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen uns dem zuwenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was heute Realit\u00e4t ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.480", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann man auch den Daten und Unterlagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die uns die Berufsverb\u00e4nde gegeben haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "entnehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.720", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese zeigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.680", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das befristete Engagement, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.840", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also die Vertr\u00e4ge kurzfristig Besch\u00e4ftigter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute in der Regel zwischen zwei Wochen und drei Monaten dauert und dass die Verdienstgrenze oft \u00fcberschritten wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "danach aber eine l\u00e4ngere Zeit folgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der man kein Einkommen hat und auf die Arbeitslosenversicherung angewiesen ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.240", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen uns mit diesen Fragen auseinandersetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.160", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen \u00c4nderungen beschlie\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.200", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in der Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.080", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der sie kurzfristig besch\u00e4ftigt sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oft hohe Betr\u00e4ge in die Arbeitslosenversicherung einzahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.920", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch einen Rechtsanspruch auf Leistungen aus der Arbeitslosenversicherung erhalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich dabei auf die Zusammenarbeit in der Koalition, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.280", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir kommen zu einem guten Ergebnis."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.160", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.600", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.120", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Schmidt.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als letztem Redner zu diesem Tagesordnungspunkt erteile ich dem Kollegen Frank Heinrich f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}